The Rune defender ornament kit is a rare reward obtained from hard Treasure Trails. It can be attached to the rune defender, making it a rune defender (t).

Once attached, the ornamented item is untradeable, but the kit can be detached from the item and sold.

The '''Rune defender ornament kit''' is a rare reward obtained from [[Clue scroll (hard)|hard]] [[Treasure Trails]]. It can be attached to the [[rune defender]], making it a [[rune defender (t)]].

Once attached, the ornamented item is untradeable, but the kit can be detached from the item and sold.
